Pergilah melayani
Tuan Panther, mengerti?

396
00:19:18.100 --> 00:19:20.340
Keparat kau,
beraninya menyinggungku?

397
00:19:20.340 --> 00:19:22.340
Dasar kepala busuk.

398
00:19:30.940 --> 00:19:32.060
Jangan lari

